<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <!-- Latest Posts -->
    <main class="post blog-post col-lg-8">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="post-single">
          <div class="post-details">
            <div class="post-meta d-flex justify-content-between">
              <div class="category">
                <h6><%= current_page.data.category %></h6>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h1><%= current_page.data.title %></h1>
            <div class="post-thumbnail">
              <img src="<%= current_page.data.image %>" alt="..." class="img-fluid">
            </div>
            <div class="sharethis-inline-share-buttons"></div>
            <div class="post-body">
              <p class="lead">
                At The HG1 Club we've collated all the places you'll find the best cocktails in Harrogate.<i>Enjoy!</i>
              </p>
              <h3>Mojo Bar</h3>
              <div class="post-thumbnail">
                <img src="<%= current_page.data.mojo_bar %>" alt="<%= current_page.data.alt_text %>" class="img-fluid">
              </div>
              <p>
                A fantastic range of cocktails with a lively atmoshpere, no matter you taste in cocktails there's something on the menu for you!
              </p>
              <p><i><a href="https://mojobar.co.uk/harrogate/drink" target="_blank">Mojo Bar</a>, Parliament St, HG1 2RE</i></p>
              <h3>Revolution de Cuba</h3>
              <div class="post-thumbnail">
                <img src="<%= current_page.data.rev_de_cuba %>" alt="<%= current_page.data.alt_text %>" class="img-fluid">
              </div>
              <p>
                A great option for anyone who wants a lively start to their night. Enjoy two for one cocktails at <strong>Revolution de <i>Cuba</i></strong>
                Monday to Friday 3-7pm as well as Saturday 5-7pm. There's also Teapots of cocktails for £12 and Mahou Lager for £3. A great way to start or finish your evening.
              </p>
              <p><i><a href="https://www.revoluciondecuba.com/bar/harrogate/" target="_blank">Revolution de Cuba</a>, 18-20 Parliament St, HG1 2RN</i></p>
              <h3>West Park Hotel</h3>
              <div class="post-thumbnail">
                <img src="<%= current_page.data.west_park %>" alt="<%= current_page.data.alt_text %>" class="img-fluid">
              </div>
              <p>
                It’s cocktail hour from <strong>5pm – 9pm!</strong> Stop by after work for the most amazing cocktails in Harrogate – over 45 cocktails, from £4.95,  deliciously refreshing and all made by hand with the freshest ingredients at fantastic prices.
                They also do a cocktail masterclass where you can learn to how to stir, shake and create a range of classic cocktails.
              </p>
              <p><i><a href="https://www.thewestparkhotel.com/events-offers/food-drink/" target="_blank">West Park Hotel</a>, 19 West Park, Harrogate, HG1 1BJ</i></p>
              <h3>Ivy Bar</h3>
              <div class="post-thumbnail">
                <img src="<%= current_page.data.ivy_bar %>" alt="<%= current_page.data.alt_text %>" class="img-fluid">
              </div>
              <p>
                As if there wasn't enough choice already for a good happy hour enjoy 2-4-1 cocktails <strong>EVERY EVENING</strong> from 5-8pm in the lively surroundings of the Ivy Bar.
              </p>
              <p><i><a href="https://www.ivoryharrogate.co.uk/news-offers-events/71461-happy-hour/" target="_blank">Ivory Bar</a>, 2 The Ginnel, Harrogate, HG1 2RB</i></p>
            </div>
            <div class="sharethis-inline-share-buttons"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    <aside class="col-lg-4">
      <!-- Widget [Search Bar Widget]-->

      <!-- Widget [Latest Posts Widget]        -->
          <div class="widget latest-posts">
            <header>
              <h3 class="h6">You also might like</h3>
            </header>
            <div>
                <% all_posts.each do |f| %>
                  <% if f.data.title.present? && f.data.published %>
                    <div class="item d-flex align-items-center">
                      <div class="image"><a href="<%= f.data.path.gsub('posts/','') %>" ><img src="<%= f.data.image %>" alt="<%= f.data.alt_text %>" class="img-fluid"></a>
                      </div>
                      <div class="title"><strong><a href="<%= f.data.path.gsub('posts/','') %>"><%= f.data.title %></a></strong>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <a></a>
                  <% end %>
                <% end %>
            </div>
          </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</div>
